{
  "stem": "22174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the High Holy Days, we went to church-- to, to temple-- to the temple.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my father with a big top hat, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but I was always bored.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one time I remember with the other-- with one of the other Jewish boys on Yom Kippur when you had-- you have to fast, you know, and be all day long in the synagogue and pray, we sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a, a big-- a factory that had burned down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we went and, and, and searched for-- for metal for, for, for, you know, metal, metal pieces to sell them, to, to sell it to the-- to a, to a, a metal place, you know, where all the metal is being-- old metal and old materials are being taken and, and eventually be recycled.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we did that and-- instead of being in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went there and, and-- to look for metal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then I-- then I-- then we kept it at home, and-- and I was always kind of concerned about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I, I don't think we ever sold it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But so we were not very religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parent were Reform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Reform, kind of.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother, she had her own personal kind of religion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She took, on, on, on Saturdays, on Shabbat, yes?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She left the store, went upstairs to our apartment, and she sat in a, in a corner of one room with a prayer book.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she prayed there, sat there and prayed by herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Her, her-- she was-- she had-- she wasn't-- in that way she was religious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was more a really deep feeling, you know, than a ritual.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
